cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new algorithm for multiple instance learning using graph neural networks. This involves learning the bag embedding by treating each bag as a graph and exploring the structural information among instances in bags. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing)
